The paper also incorporates text analysis, which suggests that it could also belong to the cs.CL (Computation and Language) category. Additionally, the paper deals with social relations, which suggests that it could belong to the cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) category. The paper also deals with information retrieval, which suggests that it could belong to the cs.IR (Information Retrieval) category.
